import React from "react"; import "./checkout.styles.scss" import {connect} from "react-redux"; import {createStructuredSelector} from 'reselect'; import { selectCartItems } from "../../redux/cart/cart.selector"; const CheckOut = ({cartItems,total})=>(
Product {cartItems.map(item=>item.name)}
Description
Quantity
Price
Remove
) const mapStatetoProps = createStructuredSelector({ cartItems :selectCartItems, total :selectCartCost }) export default connect(mapStatetoProps)(CheckOut);
